{"data":[{"name":"52:1","price":"以山岳盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلطُّورِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4736,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ṭūri ","translations":["By the Mount","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ṭūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2995]]}},{"name":"52:2","price":"以天经之书","arabic":"وَكِتَٰبٖ مَّسۡطُورٖ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4737,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wakitābin masṭūrin ","translations":["And by (the) Book","written","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wakitābin","masṭūrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1250],[2,1250,5335]]}},{"name":"52:3","price":"写于展开的皮纸者盟誓，","arabic":"فِي رَقّٖ مَّنشُورٖ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4738,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fī raqqin manshūrin ","translations":["In","parchment","unrolled","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","raqqin","manshūrin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,460],[2,460,1120],[3,1120,6345]]}},{"name":"52:4","price":"以〔众天使环游〕的天房盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلۡبَيۡتِ ٱلۡمَعۡمُورِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4739,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-bayti al-maʿmūri ","translations":["By the House","frequented","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-bayti","al-maʿmūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1110],[2,1110,3935]]}},{"name":"52:5","price":"以被升起的苍穹盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلسَّقۡفِ ٱلۡمَرۡفُوعِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4740,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-saqfi al-marfūʿi ","translations":["By the roof","raised high","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-saqfi","al-marfūʿi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,4615]]}},{"name":"52:6","price":"以汪洋的大海盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلۡبَحۡرِ ٱلۡمَسۡجُورِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4741,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-baḥri al-masjūri ","translations":["By the sea","filled","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-baḥri","al-masjūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1030],[2,1030,4865]]}},{"name":"52:7","price":"你的养主的刑罚，确是要实现的，","arabic":"إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّكَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4742,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿadhāba rabbika lawāqiʿun ","translations":["Indeed","(the) punishment","(of) your Lord","(will) surely occur","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿadhāba","rabbika","lawāqiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1260],[2,1260,2140],[3,2140,3070],[4,3070,4645]]}},{"name":"52:8","price":"是任何人不能抵抗的。","arabic":"مَّا لَهُۥ مِن دَافِعٖ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4743,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"mā lahu min dāfiʿin ","translations":["Not","for it","any","preventer","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","lahu","min","dāfiʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,1320],[3,1320,2630],[4,2630,3945]]}},{"name":"52:9","price":"在天体震动，","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَمُورُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ مَوۡرٗا","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4744,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma tamūru al-samāu mawran ","translations":["(On the) Day","will shake","the heaven","(with violent) shake","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","tamūru","al-samāu","mawran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,1610],[3,1610,4280],[4,4280,5745]]}},{"name":"52:10","price":"山岳逝去之日，","arabic":"وَتَسِيرُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ سَيۡرٗا","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4745,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"watasīru al-jibālu sayran ","translations":["And will move away","the mountains","(with an awful) movement","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["watasīru","al-jibālu","sayran",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,2200],[3,2200,3775]]}},{"name":"52:11","price":"在那日，伤哉否认〔真理〕的人们，","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4746,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fawaylun yawma-idhin lil'mukadhibīna ","translations":["Then woe","that Day","to the deniers","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["fawaylun","yawma-idhin","lil'mukadhibīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,2770],[3,2770,7175]]}},{"name":"52:12","price":"即以妄言消遣的人们！","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ فِي خَوۡضٖ يَلۡعَبُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4747,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum fī khawḍin yalʿabūna ","translations":["Who","[they]","in","(vain) discourse","are playing","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","fī","khawḍin","yalʿabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,1770],[3,1770,2210],[4,2210,3370],[5,3370,7315]]}},{"name":"52:13","price":"在那日，他们将被投入火狱。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يُدَعُّونَ إِلَىٰ نَارِ جَهَنَّمَ دَعًّا","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4748,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yudaʿʿūna ilā nāri jahannama daʿʿan ","translations":["(The) Day","they will be thrust","(in)to","(the) Fire","(of) Hell","(with) a thrust","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yudaʿʿūna","ilā","nāri","jahannama","daʿʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,660],[2,660,2080],[3,2080,2760],[4,2760,3470],[5,3470,5530],[6,5530,6595]]}},{"name":"52:14","price":"这就是你们生前所否认的火刑。","arabic":"هَٰذِهِ ٱلنَّارُ ٱلَّتِي كُنتُم بِهَا تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4749,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"hādhihi al-nāru allatī kuntum bihā tukadhibūna ","translations":["This","(is) the Fire","which","you used to","[of it]","deny","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["hādhihi","al-nāru","allatī","kuntum","bihā","tukadhibūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,2310],[3,2310,3220],[4,3220,5240],[5,5240,5880],[6,5880,6460],[7,6460,10035]]}},{"name":"52:15","price":"这是魔术呢？还是你们看不见呢？","arabic":"أَفَسِحۡرٌ هَٰذَآ أَمۡ أَنتُمۡ لَا تُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4750,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"afasiḥ'run hādhā am antum lā tub'ṣirūna ","translations":["Then is this magic","Then is this magic","or","you","(do) not","see","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["afasiḥ'run","hādhā","am","antum","lā","tub'ṣirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,3520],[3,3520,3920],[4,3920,5550],[5,5550,6000],[6,6000,9625]]}},{"name":"52:16","price":"你们进火狱去吧！你们忍受与否，那对于你们是一样的。你们只受自己行为的报酬。","arabic":"ٱصۡلَوۡهَا فَٱصۡبِرُوٓاْ أَوۡ لَا تَصۡبِرُواْ سَوَآءٌ عَلَيۡكُمۡۖ إِنَّمَا تُجۡزَوۡنَ مَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4751,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"iṣ'lawhā fa-iṣ'birū aw lā taṣbirū sawāon ʿalaykum innamā tuj'zawna mā kuntum taʿmalūna ","translations":["Burn in it","then be patient","or","(do) not","be patient","(it is) same","for you","Only","you are being recompensed","(for) what","you used to","do","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["iṣ'lawhā","fa-iṣ'birū","aw","lā","taṣbirū","sawāon","ʿalaykum","innamā","tuj'zawna","mā","kuntum","taʿmalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,4100],[3,4100,4500],[4,4500,4920],[5,4920,6020],[6,6020,6870],[7,6870,8190],[8,8190,10200],[9,10200,12020],[10,12020,13200],[11,13200,13570],[12,13570,15350],[13,15350,19125]]}},{"name":"52:17","price":"敬畏的人们，必定在乐园和恩泽中，","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ وَنَعِيمٖ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4752,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-mutaqīna fī jannātin wanaʿīmin ","translations":["Indeed","the righteous","(will be) in","Gardens","and pleasure","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-mutaqīna","fī","jannātin","wanaʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,3130],[3,3130,3610],[4,3610,6549],[5,6549,10004]]}},{"name":"52:18","price":"因他们的养主所赏赐给他们的而快乐，他们的养主使他们得免于烈火的刑罚。","arabic":"فَٰكِهِينَ بِمَآ ءَاتَىٰهُمۡ رَبُّهُمۡ وَوَقَىٰهُمۡ رَبُّهُمۡ عَذَابَ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4753,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fākihīna bimā ātāhum rabbuhum wawaqāhum rabbuhum ʿadhāba al-jaḥīmi ","translations":["Enjoying","in what","has given them","their Lord","and protected them","their Lord","(from the) punishment","(of) Hellfire","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["fākihīna","bimā","ātāhum","rabbuhum","wawaqāhum","rabbuhum","ʿadhāba","al-jaḥīmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,3430],[3,3430,4780],[4,4780,5980],[5,5980,7290],[6,7290,8420],[7,8420,9320],[8,9320,12945]]}},{"name":"52:19","price":"你们因自己的行为而愉快地吃喝吧！","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4754,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"kulū wa-ish'rabū hanīan bimā kuntum taʿmalūna ","translations":["Eat","and drink","(in) satisfaction","for what","you used to","do","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["kulū","wa-ish'rabū","hanīan","bimā","kuntum","taʿmalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,810],[2,810,1850],[3,1850,5060],[4,5060,5750],[5,5750,7590],[6,7590,10995]]}},{"name":"52:20","price":"〔他们〕靠在分列成行的床上，我将以白皙的、美目的女子做他们的伴侣。","arabic":"مُتَّكِـِٔينَ عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مَّصۡفُوفَةٖۖ وَزَوَّجۡنَٰهُم بِحُورٍ عِينٖ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4755,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"muttakiīna ʿalā sururin maṣfūfatin wazawwajnāhum biḥūrin ʿīnin ","translations":["Reclining","on","thrones","lined up","and We will marry them","to fair ones","(with) large eyes","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["muttakiīna","ʿalā","sururin","maṣfūfatin","wazawwajnāhum","biḥūrin","ʿīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1690],[2,1690,2320],[3,2320,3120],[4,3120,5830],[5,5830,8520],[6,8520,9480],[7,9480,12205]]}},{"name":"52:21","price":"自己归信，子孙也跟着归信者，我将使他们的子孙与他们同级，我不减少他们的善功一丝毫。每人应对自己的行为负责。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَٱتَّبَعَتۡهُمۡ ذُرِّيَّتُهُم بِإِيمَٰنٍ أَلۡحَقۡنَا بِهِمۡ ذُرِّيَّتَهُمۡ وَمَآ أَلَتۡنَٰهُم مِّنۡ عَمَلِهِم مِّن شَيۡءٖۚ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيِٕۭ بِمَا كَسَبَ رَهِينٞ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4756,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna āmanū wa-ittabaʿathum dhurriyyatuhum biīmānin alḥaqnā bihim dhurriyyatahum wamā alatnāhum min ʿamalihim min shayin kullu im'ri-in bimā kasaba rahīnun ","translations":["And those who","believed","and followed them","their offspring","in faith","We will join","with them","their offspring","and not","We will deprive them","of","their deeds","(in) any","thing","Every","person","for what","he earned","(is) pledged","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","āmanū","wa-ittabaʿathum","dhurriyyatuhum","biīmānin","alḥaqnā","bihim","dhurriyyatahum","wamā","alatnāhum","min","ʿamalihim","min","shayin","kullu","im'ri-in","bimā","kasaba","rahīnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1370],[2,1370,2650],[3,2650,4270],[4,4270,6820],[5,6820,8460],[6,8460,9750],[7,9750,10450],[8,10450,12260],[9,12260,14170],[10,14170,15710],[11,15710,16790],[12,16790,17850],[13,17850,20060],[14,20060,20370],[15,20370,23160],[16,23160,24180],[17,24180,25210],[18,25210,25960],[19,25960,28685]]}},{"name":"52:22","price":"我将以他们所嗜好的水果和肉食供给他们，","arabic":"وَأَمۡدَدۡنَٰهُم بِفَٰكِهَةٖ وَلَحۡمٖ مِّمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4757,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-amdadnāhum bifākihatin walaḥmin mimmā yashtahūna ","translations":["And We will provide them","with fruit","and meat","from what","they desire","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-amdadnāhum","bifākihatin","walaḥmin","mimmā","yashtahūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2560],[2,2560,4880],[3,4880,5740],[4,5740,8050],[5,8050,11385]]}},{"name":"52:23","price":"他们在乐园中互递〔酒〕杯，不出恶言，也不会犯罪恶。","arabic":"يَتَنَٰزَعُونَ فِيهَا كَأۡسٗا لَّا لَغۡوٞ فِيهَا وَلَا تَأۡثِيمٞ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4758,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"yatanāzaʿūna fīhā kasan lā laghwun fīhā walā tathīmun ","translations":["They will pass to one another","therein","a cup","no","ill speech","therein","and no","sin","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["yatanāzaʿūna","fīhā","kasan","lā","laghwun","fīhā","walā","tathīmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1690],[2,1690,2660],[3,2660,3380],[4,3380,4030],[5,4030,5550],[6,5550,6450],[7,6450,7070],[8,7070,10045]]}},{"name":"52:24","price":"他们的僮仆轮流着服侍他们，那些僮仆，好像藏在蚌壳里的珍珠一样。","arabic":"۞ وَيَطُوفُ عَلَيۡهِمۡ غِلۡمَانٞ لَّهُمۡ كَأَنَّهُمۡ لُؤۡلُؤٞ مَّكۡنُونٞ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4759,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wayaṭūfu ʿalayhim ghil'mānun lahum ka-annahum lu'lu-on maknūnun ","translations":["And will circulate","among them","boys","for them","as if they (were)","pearls","well-protected","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wayaṭūfu","ʿalayhim","ghil'mānun","lahum","ka-annahum","lu'lu-on","maknūnun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2220],[3,2220,3310],[4,3310,4240],[5,4240,6260],[6,6260,7180],[7,7180,11345]]}},{"name":"52:25","price":"于是他们大家走向前来互相谈论。","arabic":"وَأَقۡبَلَ بَعۡضُهُمۡ عَلَىٰ بَعۡضٖ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4760,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-aqbala baʿḍuhum ʿalā baʿḍin yatasāalūna ","translations":["And will approach","some of them","to","others","inquiring","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-aqbala","baʿḍuhum","ʿalā","baʿḍin","yatasāalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,2200],[3,2200,2880],[4,2880,4670],[5,4670,10055]]}},{"name":"52:26","price":"他们将说：“以前我们为自己的家属确是战战兢兢的，","arabic":"قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّا كُنَّا قَبۡلُ فِيٓ أَهۡلِنَا مُشۡفِقِينَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4761,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"qālū innā kunnā qablu fī ahlinā mush'fiqīna ","translations":["They will say","Indeed, we","[we] were","before","among","our families","fearful","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["qālū","innā","kunnā","qablu","fī","ahlinā","mush'fiqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2390],[2,2390,3770],[3,3770,5180],[4,5180,5910],[5,5910,7600],[6,7600,8730],[7,8730,11865]]}},{"name":"52:27","price":"但安拉已施恩于我们，并使我们得免于毒风的刑罚。","arabic":"فَمَنَّ ٱللَّهُ عَلَيۡنَا وَوَقَىٰنَا عَذَابَ ٱلسَّمُومِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4762,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"famanna al-lahu ʿalaynā wawaqānā ʿadhāba al-samūmi ","translations":["But Allah conferred favor","But Allah conferred favor","upon us","and protected us","(from the) punishment","(of) the Scorching Fire","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["famanna","al-lahu","ʿalaynā","wawaqānā","ʿadhāba","al-samūmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,2560],[3,2560,3610],[4,3610,5060],[5,5060,5940],[6,5940,9845]]}},{"name":"52:28","price":"以前我们的确常常祈祷他，他确是仁爱的，确是至慈的。”","arabic":"إِنَّا كُنَّا مِن قَبۡلُ نَدۡعُوهُۖ إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ ٱلۡبَرُّ ٱلرَّحِيمُ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4763,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"innā kunnā min qablu nadʿūhu innahu huwa al-baru al-raḥīmu ","translations":["Indeed, we","[we] used to","before","before","call Him","Indeed, He","[He]","(is) the Most Kind","the Most Merciful","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["innā","kunnā","min","qablu","nadʿūhu","innahu","huwa","al-baru","al-raḥīmu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1440],[2,1440,3010],[3,3010,4210],[4,4210,4810],[5,4810,8270],[6,8270,10020],[7,10020,10410],[8,10410,11590],[9,11590,14555]]}},{"name":"52:29","price":"你应当教诲众人，因为借你的养主的恩典，你不是一个占卜者，也不是一个疯人。","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ فَمَآ أَنتَ بِنِعۡمَتِ رَبِّكَ بِكَاهِنٖ وَلَا مَجۡنُونٍ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4764,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhakkir famā anta biniʿ'mati rabbika bikāhinin walā majnūnin ","translations":["Therefore remind","for not","you","(are) by (the) grace","(of) your Lord","a soothsayer","and not","a madman","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhakkir","famā","anta","biniʿ'mati","rabbika","bikāhinin","walā","majnūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,3230],[3,3230,4730],[4,4730,5830],[5,5830,6760],[6,6760,8830],[7,8830,9440],[8,9440,12785]]}},{"name":"52:30","price":"不然，他们说：“他是一个诗人，我们等待他遭逢厄运。”","arabic":"أَمۡ يَقُولُونَ شَاعِرٞ نَّتَرَبَّصُ بِهِۦ رَيۡبَ ٱلۡمَنُونِ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4765,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am yaqūlūna shāʿirun natarabbaṣu bihi rayba al-manūni ","translations":["Or","(do) they say","A poet","we wait","for him","a misfortune of time","a misfortune of time","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["am","yaqūlūna","shāʿirun","natarabbaṣu","bihi","rayba","al-manūni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,480],[2,480,1770],[3,1770,2860],[4,2860,4870],[5,4870,5480],[6,5480,6110],[7,6110,8995]]}},{"name":"52:31","price":"你说：“你们等待吧！我确是与你们一同等待的。”","arabic":"قُلۡ تَرَبَّصُواْ فَإِنِّي مَعَكُم مِّنَ ٱلۡمُتَرَبِّصِينَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4766,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"qul tarabbaṣū fa-innī maʿakum mina al-mutarabiṣīna ","translations":["Say","Wait","for indeed I am","with you","among","those who wait","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","tarabbaṣū","fa-innī","maʿakum","mina","al-mutarabiṣīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,540],[2,540,1910],[3,1910,3860],[4,3860,4810],[5,4810,5950],[6,5950,9975]]}},{"name":"52:32","price":"难道他们的理智命令他们说这句话吗？不然，他们是放荡的民众。","arabic":"أَمۡ تَأۡمُرُهُمۡ أَحۡلَٰمُهُم بِهَٰذَآۚ أَمۡ هُمۡ قَوۡمٞ طَاغُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4767,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am tamuruhum aḥlāmuhum bihādhā am hum qawmun ṭāghūna ","translations":["Or","command them","their minds","this","or","they","(are) a people","transgressing","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["am","tamuruhum","aḥlāmuhum","bihādhā","am","hum","qawmun","ṭāghūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,480],[2,480,1870],[3,1870,3660],[4,3660,5350],[5,5350,6200],[6,6200,6640],[7,6640,8360],[8,8360,11725]]}},{"name":"52:33","price":"难道他们说他曾捏造它吗？不然，其实是他们不归信。","arabic":"أَمۡ يَقُولُونَ تَقَوَّلَهُۥۚ بَل لَّا يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4768,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am yaqūlūna taqawwalahu bal lā yu'minūna ","translations":["Or","(do) they say","He has made it up","Nay","not","they believe","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["am","yaqūlūna","taqawwalahu","bal","lā","yu'minūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,390],[2,390,1870],[3,1870,3630],[4,3630,3870],[5,3870,4580],[6,4580,7565]]}},{"name":"52:34","price":"叫他们作出像这样的文辞来，如果他们是说实话的！","arabic":"فَلۡيَأۡتُواْ بِحَدِيثٖ مِّثۡلِهِۦٓ إِن كَانُواْ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4769,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"falyatū biḥadīthin mith'lihi in kānū ṣādiqīna ","translations":["Then let them bring","a statement","like it","if","they are","truthful","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["falyatū","biḥadīthin","mith'lihi","in","kānū","ṣādiqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1330],[2,1330,2490],[3,2490,5580],[4,5580,6650],[5,6650,7500],[6,7500,10875]]}},{"name":"52:35","price":"是他们从无到有被创造出来呢？还是他们自己就是创造者呢？","arabic":"أَمۡ خُلِقُواْ مِنۡ غَيۡرِ شَيۡءٍ أَمۡ هُمُ ٱلۡخَٰلِقُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4770,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am khuliqū min ghayri shayin am humu al-khāliqūna ","translations":["Or","they were created","of","nothing","nothing","or","(are) they","the creators","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["am","khuliqū","min","ghayri","shayin","am","humu","al-khāliqūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1350],[3,1350,1780],[4,1780,2410],[5,2410,3370],[6,3370,3770],[7,3770,4190],[8,4190,7755]]}},{"name":"52:36","price":"难道他们曾创造天地吗？不然，是他们不确信〔安拉〕。","arabic":"أَمۡ خَلَقُواْ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضَۚ بَل لَّا يُوقِنُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4771,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am khalaqū al-samāwāti wal-arḍa bal lā yūqinūna ","translations":["Or","(did) they create","the heavens","and the earth","Nay","not","they are certain","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["am","khalaqū","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍa","bal","lā","yūqinūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,1130],[3,1130,2750],[4,2750,4240],[5,4240,4510],[6,4510,5170],[7,5170,8475]]}},{"name":"52:37","price":"是你的养主的库藏归他们掌管呢？还是他们是那些库藏的监督呢？","arabic":"أَمۡ عِندَهُمۡ خَزَآئِنُ رَبِّكَ أَمۡ هُمُ ٱلۡمُصَۜيۡطِرُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4772,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am ʿindahum khazāinu rabbika am humu al-muṣayṭirūna ","translations":["Or","with them","(are the) treasures","(of) your Lord","or","(are) they","the controllers","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["am","ʿindahum","khazāinu","rabbika","am","humu","al-muṣayṭirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,2210],[3,2210,5140],[4,5140,6070],[5,6070,6460],[6,6460,6850],[7,6850,10945]]}},{"name":"52:38","price":"难道他们有一架天梯，可以〔登上〕去倾听吗？叫他们中的倾听者拿一个明证来吧！","arabic":"أَمۡ لَهُمۡ سُلَّمٞ يَسۡتَمِعُونَ فِيهِۖ فَلۡيَأۡتِ مُسۡتَمِعُهُم بِسُلۡطَٰنٖ مُّبِينٍ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4773,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am lahum sullamun yastamiʿūna fīhi falyati mus'tamiʿuhum bisul'ṭānin mubīnin ","translations":["Or","for them","(is) a stairway","they listen","therewith","Then let bring","their listener","an authority","clear","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lahum","sullamun","yastamiʿūna","fīhi","falyati","mus'tamiʿuhum","bisul'ṭānin","mubīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,520],[2,520,1110],[3,1110,2030],[4,2030,4680],[5,4680,6990],[6,6990,8050],[7,8050,10290],[8,10290,11480],[9,11480,15225]]}},{"name":"52:39","price":"难道女儿归他〔安拉〕，而儿子却归你们吗？","arabic":"أَمۡ لَهُ ٱلۡبَنَٰتُ وَلَكُمُ ٱلۡبَنُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4774,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am lahu al-banātu walakumu al-banūna ","translations":["Or","for Him","(are) daughters","while for you","(are) sons","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lahu","al-banātu","walakumu","al-banūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,880],[3,880,2150],[4,2150,2900],[5,2900,6185]]}},{"name":"52:40","price":"难道你向他们索取报酬，故他们为债务而担负太重？","arabic":"أَمۡ تَسۡـَٔلُهُمۡ أَجۡرٗا فَهُم مِّن مَّغۡرَمٖ مُّثۡقَلُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4775,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am tasaluhum ajran fahum min maghramin muth'qalūna ","translations":["Or","(do) you ask from them","a payment","so they","from","a debt","(are) overburdened","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["am","tasaluhum","ajran","fahum","min","maghramin","muth'qalūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1740],[3,1740,3420],[4,3420,3960],[5,3960,5030],[6,5030,6790],[7,6790,11205]]}},{"name":"52:41","price":"难道他们能知幽玄，故能将它记录下来？","arabic":"أَمۡ عِندَهُمُ ٱلۡغَيۡبُ فَهُمۡ يَكۡتُبُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4776,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am ʿindahumu al-ghaybu fahum yaktubūna ","translations":["Or","with them","(is) the unseen","so they","write (it) down","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["am","ʿindahumu","al-ghaybu","fahum","yaktubūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,440],[2,440,2510],[3,2510,3460],[4,3460,4210],[5,4210,7655]]}},{"name":"52:42","price":"难道他们欲用计谋吗？不归信者，将自中其计。","arabic":"أَمۡ يُرِيدُونَ كَيۡدٗاۖ فَٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ هُمُ ٱلۡمَكِيدُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4777,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am yurīdūna kaydan fa-alladhīna kafarū humu al-makīdūna ","translations":["Or","(do) they intend","a plot","But those who","disbelieve","themselves","(are in) the plot","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["am","yurīdūna","kaydan","fa-alladhīna","kafarū","humu","al-makīdūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1610],[3,1610,2770],[4,2770,4480],[5,4480,5380],[6,5380,5810],[7,5810,9875]]}},{"name":"52:43","price":"难道除安拉外，他们还有别的神灵吗？安拉是超乎他们所用以配他的。","arabic":"أَمۡ لَهُمۡ إِلَٰهٌ غَيۡرُ ٱللَّهِۚ سُبۡحَٰنَ ٱللَّهِ عَمَّا يُشۡرِكُونَ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4778,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"am lahum ilāhun ghayru al-lahi sub'ḥāna al-lahi ʿammā yush'rikūna ","translations":["Or","for them","a god","other than","Allah","Glory be","(to) Allah","from what","they associate (with Him)","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["am","lahum","ilāhun","ghayru","al-lahi","sub'ḥāna","al-lahi","ʿammā","yush'rikūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,270],[2,270,1120],[3,1120,2120],[4,2120,2860],[5,2860,6440],[6,6440,7520],[7,7520,8510],[8,8510,10150],[9,10150,13475]]}},{"name":"52:44","price":"如果他们看见天掉下来一块，他们将说：“这是成堆的云彩。”","arabic":"وَإِن يَرَوۡاْ كِسۡفٗا مِّنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ سَاقِطٗا يَقُولُواْ سَحَابٞ مَّرۡكُومٞ","category":["52 (At-Tur)","At-Tur","Surah At-Tur"],"ayahNumber":4779,"juzNumber":27,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-in yaraw kis'fan mina al-samāi sāqiṭan yaqūlū saḥābun markūmun ","translations":["And if","they were to see","a portion","from","the sky","falling","they will say","Clouds","h